attributes.Long form description: The student is instructed to manipulate a dslr. First, the student will inspect the dslr, then detach the lens, and attach them back. Then, detach the lens cover and attach them back, turn on and off the dslr, remove the battery, insert it back, and remove the sd card and insert it back.
